following representation:
\deqn{
  {(-1)}^{k-1} \Delta^{k} \psi(x)
    = \int_{0}^{\infty} e^{-ux} {(1 - e^{-u})}^{k}
      \frac{e^{-au}}{u} du, x>0, k>0.
}

